data.title: Why did braceface get cancelled?
data.meta_description:
Braceface got cancelled because apparently it didn't get enough
ratings. I looked up all these people loved this show and now i
have to watch it on YouTube, not only that but they had to put
shows like Hannah Montana (luckily that show is over) and all these
actors and actresses that are a bad influence to children, this
show is at least a cartoon with professional adults.
data.text:
Braceface got cancelled because apparently it didn't get enough ratings. I looked up all these people loved this show and now i have to watch it on YouTube, not only that but they had to put shows like Hannah Montana (luckily that show is over) and all these actors and actresses that are a bad influence to children, this show is at least a cartoon with professional adults.

Why was My Friends Tigger and Pooh cancelled?

There was no information provided by Disney as to why they cancelled the show.Most likely it was cancelled for the same reason most shows are cancelled, the ratings didn't justify the cost of producing new episodes.
